    "created_at": "2026-03-19T00:00:00.000Z",
    "notes": "Key improvements: (1) Global VIX<20 entry gate \u2014 no new position in panic markets. (2) Priority-1 panic rule: 30s cooldown, fires when any leg delta >=0.65 before the standard adj gets a chance. (3) VIX spike defense rule: widens both legs to 0.15 delta when VIX>=20, 5min cooldown prevents churn. (4) Standard adj now has cooldown raised to 90s and explicitly excludes VIX>=20 environment. (5) Trailing SL: locks \u20b92000, trails \u20b91000 steps every \u20b91000 gain \u2014 no more giving back all premium. (6) Breakeven buffer: exit if spot within 50pts of breakeven. (7) Hard VIX=25 exit condition \u2014 handles war/event spike scenarios."
  },
